headline: Can Hasbro’s (HAS) Digital Expansion Truly Refresh Its Legacy Brand Portfolio?
summary: Recently at New York Comic Con, Kayou and Hasbro showcased the MY LITTLE PONY Card Game – Friendships Begin, while several digital and collectible product announcements as well as new international e-commerce partnerships highlighted Hasbro's ongoing push into diverse markets and channels. This multi-pronged approach highlights how Hasbro is blending legacy brands with digital expansion and global partnerships to capture new audience segments and recurring revenue streams.
